snippet.textDisplay: See, I remember Adrienne as being this 15 year old diva who could SANG her butt off , who performed years beyond her age.  I always thought her voice was dope, and the only reason I liked 3LW. Beautiful, open, sultry, and light tones. When did she become so insecure? She came back to life to me when I saw clips of her on Masked Singer. I miss that Adrienne, the one who didn’t need a mask. Girl, own you. Who cares what people think about your voice as long as your voice sounds beautiful to you!
